data.oai_dc:dc: Eumycetozoa.com is an on-line taxonomic checklist and nomenclatural information system of the Eumycetozoans of the world (Myxomycetes, Dictyostelids and Protostelids). It provides information on 1,218 species, 2,487 synonyms and 1,004 invalid or doubtful names employed in this group. The database can be searched by different ranks, it can show the history of the name, all synonyms of the species, taxonomic views in different publications, or the single view of the Eumycetozoa.com editors.
